title: C-O Segemyhr Season 1-3
description: This is an old Swedish TV show that is called C/O Segemyhr, which aired between 1998-2004. I've tried to get it on different torrent sites for quite a long time, but last night I got tired of not getting it so I tried to search for it on YouTube, where I hit the jackpot. I downloaded season 1-3 and this is also the seasons in this torrent (there is actually a total of five seasons). I decided to upload this TV show because I personally believe we cannot afford to loose this treasure-chest of a 1990's TV shows. I will also upload these three seasons one by one for people who either just need one or two seasons, or simply wants to download each season one by one. I will also complete the TV show with the two last season (season 4-5) within a short amount of time.
